And I prayed over them and prayed for them, you know.

01:01:17.920 --> 01:01:27.661
People have the valley; He said we would walk through it, He didn't say that we wouldn't experience it at all.

01:01:38.263 --> 01:01:38.605
In the valley of the shadow of death, we will fear no evil.

01:01:41.348 --> 01:01:48.511
And when you go through those valleys in life, like when we've been with Megan and we see these people and they go, 'Man, we're having all these issues and the valley is hard,' it's real.

01:01:48.511 --> 01:01:48.943
It's real.

01:01:50.870 --> 01:01:56.789
And I think a lot of times—I don't like the 'spiritual' people, and a lot of times in the circles that we're familiar with, they don't tell you about the struggle that much.

01:01:56.789 --> 01:01:59.120
They don't tell you about how their body is overcoming.

01:01:59.120 --> 01:02:01.119
They won't even talk about it.

01:02:11.010 --> 01:02:11.180
They won't tell you what's going on with their lives because they don't want to; they don't speak it out, of course.

01:02:11.180 --> 01:02:16.928
But a lot of times, I feel like it does a disservice.

01:02:19.337 --> 01:02:34.026
You need to know how to believe God through your valley, how to speak to your mountain when you're going through, and the storms of life are coming, and you've got a hurricane all the way around you, and you feel like you're the only one going through it.

01:02:34.026 --> 01:02:38.440
I'm telling you, there's a lot of people going through a lot of stuff.

01:02:38.440 --> 01:02:42.470
They may not always talk about it, but everyone has their stuff.

01:02:42.470 --> 01:02:44.640
Everybody has stuff they're going through.

01:02:44.640 --> 01:02:46.507
We're still walking through ours.

01:02:46.507 --> 01:02:47.657
We're believing God.

01:02:47.657 --> 01:02:49.440
Megan's getting better and better, y'all.

01:02:49.440 --> 01:02:51.240
We're believing God for Megan.

01:03:05.133 --> 01:03:09.712
And there are other things we're believing for.

01:03:09.712 --> 01:03:13.943
Don't sit there and go, 'Well, it's just Megan.

01:03:13.943 --> 01:03:17.520
' No, we're believing for a lot of things.

01:03:17.520 --> 01:03:27.771
But I want to tell you, after you come across some of the people that we did this week, we're just human just like you all are.

01:03:33.160 --> 01:03:33.329
And we're excited, you're excited, but I want to tell you, we put our pants on just the same way you do.

01:03:33.329 --> 01:03:35.268
We eat the same thing you do.

01:03:35.268 --> 01:03:38.720
We take a bath because we stink just like you do.

01:03:38.720 --> 01:03:47.119
And I'm going to tell you that if Jesus can do it for us, and where He's brought us out of...

01:03:47.119 --> 01:03:52.900
being where I was, as I was sitting in that auditorium, I used to clean it.

01:03:52.900 --> 01:03:55.439
I would spend hours cleaning it.

01:03:55.439 --> 01:03:57.839
I would spend hours cleaning all the bathrooms.

01:03:58.666 --> 01:04:04.799
And I glean from where I used to be and where God has brought us now.

01:04:04.799 --> 01:04:11.217
If He could do it for me, ladies and gentlemen, He can do it for you.

01:04:11.217 --> 01:04:19.626
If Jesus can touch my life and turn my mess into a message, I'm telling you, He can turn your mess into a message.

01:04:19.626 --> 01:04:22.959
If you just be willing and obedient, you'll eat the good of the land.

01:04:23.360 --> 01:04:26.301
And I'm telling you, it's where it came from: a seed at a time.

01:04:26.301 --> 01:04:37.520
When we used to say, 'God, if I sow a dollar, if I had a dollar, if I sowed $5, if I had whatever, I believe Him for a harvest to be where I'm at right now.

01:04:37.520 --> 01:04:44.240
' And it took years, but it's the faith of persistence and saying, 'I believe that God's going to turn this around.

01:04:44.240 --> 01:04:50.000
' And it doesn't happen overnight a lot of times.

01:04:59.760 --> 01:05:00.080
It's the drip that keeps on dripping on that rock that makes the indentation in a cave over how long?

01:05:00.080 --> 01:05:01.940
A long time.

01:05:01.940 --> 01:05:05.359
It's the drip that keeps on dripping, one at a time.

01:05:05.359 --> 01:05:08.648
It's how many times you confess it.

01:05:08.648 --> 01:05:10.230
How many times do you pray over it?

01:05:10.230 --> 01:05:12.000
How many times you keep knocking, you keep pursuing?

01:05:12.000 --> 01:05:15.313
If you keep seeking, if you keep going...

01:05:28.676 --> 01:05:28.844
and it's like people go, 'Well, I've prayed over it, Brandon, for a couple of days.

01:05:28.844 --> 01:05:30.587
' Try 25, twenty-some years for something!

01:05:38.279 --> 01:05:38.539
You sit there and you pray over something and you don't see anything.

01:05:38.539 --> 01:05:47.320
For the first couple of years, you're going, 'Man, I know I'm gaining ground,' but you may not see it in the natural too much.

01:05:52.746 --> 01:05:53.040
And then all of a sudden, those roots that went so deep into the ground...

01:05:54.213 --> 01:05:58.448
I told her, I said, 'It's how long it takes for a bamboo.

01:06:04.133 --> 01:06:04.596
The roots go way down for a long time, and then all of a sudden it has radical growth.

01:06:04.596 --> 01:06:05.289
Radical growth.

01:06:05.289 --> 01:06:12.340
' But you never see the roots growing down because it's getting a foundation.

01:06:19.039 --> 01:06:19.280
And that's where a lot of you are: you're getting your foundation.

01:06:21.626 --> 01:06:26.720
Your roots are growing down in faith; your roots are growing down, and you're about to see an explosion of growth coming upward.

01:06:26.720 --> 01:06:32.833
Everybody's going to see it overnight, and they're going to say, 'Boy, you are an overnight success.

01:06:32.833 --> 01:06:37.050
' You say, 'No, you don't know how far my root went down.

01:06:37.050 --> 01:06:40.026
You don't know how far my root went down.

01:06:40.026 --> 01:06:49.160
' And I'm just going to tell you, it's time for you to not give up on what you've been believing for.

01:06:49.160 --> 01:06:50.150
Be persistent.

01:06:50.150 --> 01:06:57.619
We are; we're still believing, even in the midst of all our stuff we go through, and people won't have a clue.

01:06:57.619 --> 01:06:58.693
Fight the good fight.

01:07:00.080 --> 01:07:05.910
This whole thing's new to us—this side of the coin of it, is what I'm going to say.

01:07:05.910 --> 01:07:22.091
We were the grunts for a long time: the janitors, the person counting the offerings, opening the letters and counting the offerings, reading the letters, putting the data in there.

01:07:22.091 --> 01:07:25.813
We did it for twenty-some years.

01:07:31.946 --> 01:07:32.320
And then to be on this side of it is a lot of spiritual pressure.

01:07:37.280 --> 01:07:39.253
The Lord told me, He said, 'I brought you to another place to die even more.

01:07:48.079 --> 01:07:50.799
You thought you died back there as a janitor; this is even more of a death—dying to self when you feel, "Well, I have this and I have that," and people should honor that.

01:07:50.799 --> 01:07:53.577
' And then the Lord said, 'Die to that.

01:07:53.577 --> 01:07:54.733
Die to that.

01:07:54.733 --> 01:07:57.428
Go back to being like the janitor.

01:08:07.239 --> 01:08:07.459
You clean and do exactly what I've called you to do.

01:08:07.459 --> 01:08:08.339
Keep cultivating that.

01:08:08.339 --> 01:08:11.376
' I'm telling you folks, you die at every level.

01:08:17.013 --> 01:08:17.280
You die at every level.

01:08:17.280 --> 01:08:20.359
Dying to self is what I'm talking about—dying to self.

01:08:23.222 --> 01:08:29.399
And you think, 'Well, I'm going to get over this, and I've got this now,' and the Lord says, 'No, do you see that area right there?

01:08:29.399 --> 01:08:32.835
You're going to have to die a little bit more in that area right there.

01:08:32.835 --> 01:08:33.316
Surrender.

01:08:33.316 --> 01:08:34.142
Keep surrendering.

01:08:34.142 --> 01:08:37.508
' But we're going to take communion and pray.

01:08:37.508 --> 01:08:39.660
Do you want to pray with us?

01:08:39.660 --> 01:08:40.920
You can pray with us.

01:08:40.920 --> 01:08:42.320
How many people here?

01:08:42.320 --> 01:08:43.220
Oh, 4,443.

01:08:43.220 --> 01:08:46.400
Father, we just thank You for the body right now.

01:08:46.400 --> 01:08:53.325
We lift it up before You, Father, and we thank You for all that You've done for us, for this is the meal that heals.

01:09:05.060 --> 01:09:05.240
And we believe, Father, that we receive what we're believing for right now, that by His stripes we're healed.

01:09:05.240 --> 01:09:07.480
Every single one of us, I'm sure, has something we're believing for.

01:09:07.480 --> 01:09:13.085
So, Father, right now, Diana and I are in agreement with them that we'll be there, too.

01:09:18.227 --> 01:09:18.533
That everything they put their hands to will prosper.

01:09:18.533 --> 01:09:20.259
Everything they touch is overflow.

01:09:20.259 --> 01:09:26.079
Father, this is a season of when You show up and show off in our lives, God.

01:09:28.299 --> 01:09:40.239
And we believe right now in the name of Jesus that we're healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus in every area of our lives—spiritually, physically, financially—and we take this body in the name of Jesus, and we give You all the glory, honor, and praise for it.

01:09:40.239 --> 01:09:40.915
Amen and amen.

01:09:40.915 --> 01:09:41.590
Thank you, Lord.

01:09:41.590 --> 01:09:44.480
Now, Lord, we plead the blood of Jesus over us, Father, as we pray.

01:09:44.480 --> 01:09:50.409
We plead the blood over our eyes and over our ears, and over us, that we hear Your voice and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

01:09:50.409 --> 01:09:56.960
We take authority over the demonic spirits that would try to snare us in any way, and we just lift up this time of prayer.

01:09:58.239 --> 01:10:02.090
And we thank You, Lord, that we hear You, and Father, You show us that which is to come in the name of Jesus.

01:10:02.409 --> 01:10:03.910
And we plead the blood over our sins today, God.

01:10:08.200 --> 01:10:12.869
You said if we confess our sins, you are faithful and just to forgive us of our sins and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

01:10:17.730 --> 01:10:17.920
And Father, we believe right now in the name of Jesus that all our sins are washed in the blood.

01:10:22.747 --> 01:10:22.889
And we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:10:22.889 --> 01:10:30.526
And we plead the blood of Jesus over us right now—all around this house, all around our children, all around our finances, all around our car, all around everything.

01:10:45.040 --> 01:10:45.220
I cover us in the blood in the name of Jesus.

01:10:47.829 --> 01:10:50.023
And I thank you, Lord, for what you've done for us by that blood.

01:10:50.023 --> 01:10:51.623
Amen and amen.

01:10:51.623 --> 01:10:53.147
That's how we take communion.

01:11:03.182 --> 01:11:03.484
You say, 'Well, that's not right.

01:11:03.484 --> 01:11:05.863
' Well, that's how we do it.

01:11:05.863 --> 01:11:12.533
I told Diana when we were praying, we were talking about how the Lord started showing us about prosperity in your soul.

01:11:12.533 --> 01:11:17.600
'Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

01:11:17.600 --> 01:11:22.053
' And he said, 'Brandon, you can take herbs, all these things.

01:11:22.053 --> 01:11:29.640
' He gave us all these different vitamins and all these things at the health food store to try to help us, right?

01:11:36.560 --> 01:11:36.777
But he said, 'You can take that, and take that, and take that, and still be sick because why?

01:11:36.777 --> 01:11:40.970
You're not prosperous in your soul, in your mind, your will, and emotions.

01:11:40.970 --> 01:11:48.533
' 'Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

01:11:48.533 --> 01:12:02.596
' But if your soul's not prospering, you're not going to be walking in health like you should, because you're always going to have all these issues.

01:12:02.596 --> 01:12:05.787
'And as the man thinketh in his heart, so is he.

01:12:05.787 --> 01:12:18.240
' And if you're thinking in your heart, you know, you've got anxiety, you've got worry, you've got depression, you've got all this stuff going on, it's affecting your cortisol levels.

01:12:18.240 --> 01:12:23.349
It's affecting all this stuff going on inside of you because you're meditating on the wrong thing.

01:12:29.410 --> 01:12:42.959
And the more you get in this word and you renew your mind by the word of God, this is what's going to change you from the inside out.

01:12:42.959 --> 01:12:54.080
If you get this word down inside of you and you start quoting it, you don't just have it in your thoughts just by your thoughts.

01:12:54.080 --> 01:12:54.660
Why?

01:12:54.660 --> 01:12:58.159
Because 'as a man thinketh in his heart, so is he.

01:12:58.159 --> 01:13:07.406
' As you speak it, you're a speaking spirit, speaking that out of your mouth, and you're changing your circumstances because your mountain needs to hear your voice.

01:13:07.406 --> 01:13:10.760
You have to speak to your mountain.

01:13:10.760 --> 01:13:29.750
So, as you prosper in your soul, as you get the word of God inside of your heart, your mind, your will, and your emotions, and you renew your mind by the word of God, that word's going to change you, and it's going to make you prosperous in your soul.

01:13:32.354 --> 01:13:35.679
It's going to prosper in your mind, your will, and your emotions because you're renewing your mind.

01:13:35.679 --> 01:13:44.582
Because of the washing of the water of the word, you've got to wash your mind.

01:13:44.582 --> 01:13:57.360
You've got to wash it, and you've got to put this on your lips, you've got to put it in your eyes, and it will change you from the inside out.

01:14:03.780 --> 01:14:10.533
And that's why I told her that we were talking about how people are, you know, overcoming, overcoming, overcoming, and you take these things, but you're not getting any better.

01:14:19.590 --> 01:14:19.900
And I'm not ever going to give the glory to an herb.

01:14:19.900 --> 01:14:20.520
No.

01:14:20.520 --> 01:14:23.486
But people are always saying, 'I've got this thing right here.

01:14:23.486 --> 01:14:27.234
You take this, and you take that, and whatever, and it's going to make you better.

01:14:27.234 --> 01:14:31.947
' And they don't get better, and you go, 'Whoa, what's going on?

01:14:31.947 --> 01:14:42.880
' Well, if you change your thinking, if you change the way you think and get this word down inside of you, it will change you from the inside out.

01:14:42.880 --> 01:14:47.235
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

01:14:54.533 --> 01:14:54.720
And so as you do that, you become an expert at the word.

01:15:00.388 --> 01:15:05.350
It's like when you go to the gym and you are able to lift five pounds, and then a couple of days later you increase it to ten maybe, and then go to fifteen.

01:15:10.537 --> 01:15:10.743
It's a day-to-day process.

01:15:10.743 --> 01:15:12.509
It's not just a one and done.

01:15:12.509 --> 01:15:15.211
It's how many times you dip in that river every day.

01:15:15.211 --> 01:15:15.554
Consistency.

01:15:15.554 --> 01:15:15.896
Yes.

01:15:15.896 --> 01:15:17.800
By having those flashcards, Diana...

01:15:32.070 --> 01:15:32.300
We put the flashcards on the mirror or on your window.

01:15:32.300 --> 01:15:42.013
You could put it wherever you're going to walk and be at the most, at the refrigerator for some, or on your TV.

01:15:42.013 --> 01:15:47.509
On your TV, have scripture, on your remote, on your phone, yeah.

01:15:47.509 --> 01:15:57.977
But whatever it is, let it get through your eyes, wherever the most common place, maybe the bathroom, having it where you see it and you're meditating on that word.

01:16:01.570 --> 01:16:02.070
And it changes you because that's the word that's going to work for you.

01:16:02.070 --> 01:16:18.506
I don't know how many times when we are praying in the spirit and you don't see anything and you're going, 'Man,' and the Lord told me, he said, 'Brandon, if ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

01:16:18.506 --> 01:16:20.845
' So that's concerning prayer.

01:16:20.845 --> 01:16:25.199
So if you want your prayer life to change, you have to...

01:16:25.199 --> 01:16:34.880
'If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

01:16:34.880 --> 01:16:53.080
' If you don't have your prayer life changing and you don't see manifestation of what you're praying for all the time, find scripture that pertains to what you're believing for and get that in there and put it in the prayer.

01:16:53.080 --> 01:16:54.760
Put it in the prayer.

01:16:54.760 --> 01:17:00.870
And I've said this before, but you need to know it: 'Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

01:17:00.870 --> 01:17:09.840
' And that's the only way you're ever going to get your life changed is by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

01:17:09.840 --> 01:17:19.680
So you put that word down inside of you, and the more you read it and the more you say it, the more it's going to change because it starts to become rhema to yourself.

01:17:20.320 --> 01:17:20.800
It comes rhema, and it goes...

01:17:34.672 --> 01:17:34.864
I read scripture and I go, 'Man,' you just know whenever you've got that knowing that you know this scripture has become real to me.

01:17:34.864 --> 01:17:39.107
Ephesians: 'the eyes of your understanding become enlightened to the things of God, to spiritual things.

01:17:39.107 --> 01:17:47.451
' So I believe with all my heart that's what changes you, and that's what's going to increase your prayer life.

01:17:47.451 --> 01:17:52.400
It's not about praying in tongues all the time or praying in English.

01:17:53.360 --> 01:17:57.589
I prayed, brother, because I told Diana, I said, 'You know, you're always looking for the glory.

01:17:57.589 --> 01:18:05.307
Where is it at with the presence of the Lord?

01:18:05.307 --> 01:18:18.549
' Because I want to lay hands on people and see them fall out, and the power of God hit them and everything, and you're going, 'Man, Lord, where is that?

01:18:18.549 --> 01:18:20.592
Where is it?

01:18:20.592 --> 01:18:24.960
' It's getting a foundation of the word inside of you, renewing your mind, getting that inside.

01:18:24.960 --> 01:18:38.820
Because I could pray all day for two hours a day in tongues, three hours a day in tongues, four hours a day, and there is no glory.

01:18:39.070 --> 01:18:51.582
I could read my Bible all the time and read it for hours and hours, and go, 'Well, I have my Bible playing in my head all day long.

01:18:51.582 --> 01:18:55.230
' But it's the truth, you know, that will set you free.

01:18:55.230 --> 01:19:00.400
It's not about how much scripture you read; it's about how much you retain.

01:19:00.400 --> 01:19:01.976
How much are you retaining?

01:19:01.976 --> 01:19:03.920
How much are you using against the devil?

01:19:03.920 --> 01:19:08.360
It's a sword when it comes out of your mouth and you know it.

01:19:08.360 --> 01:19:27.884
When I told you I had that visitation from the devil, and he came in, and I was laying in bed and Diana was asleep, and the whole house lit up like a light bulb with this dingy, dark, evil, and he offered me everything that I could ever dream of—money, finances, boats, houses, everything.

01:19:27.884 --> 01:19:37.048
He said, 'If you serve me and use the gift that you have on your life for seeing, doing things,' he said, 'I'll make you richer beyond your wildest imagination.

01:19:37.048 --> 01:19:38.276
' He showed me.

01:19:40.779 --> 01:19:40.989
I saw his palace.

01:19:43.199 --> 01:19:43.439
I saw the throne room.

01:19:53.822 --> 01:19:54.071
I saw it was black onyx with blood flowing through this thing.

01:19:54.071 --> 01:19:55.137
It was all demonic.

01:19:55.137 --> 01:20:00.469
This whole experience, I was in the most fear I've ever felt in all my life.

01:20:11.840 --> 01:20:12.080
And I was praying in the spirit.

01:20:14.240 --> 01:20:15.451
I said, "Shut up," and he was just laughing at me.

01:20:15.451 --> 01:20:17.680
He sounded like Michael Jackson off Thriller.

01:20:17.680 --> 01:20:26.159
He was laughing at me because he was offering all this stuff and I said, "I'll never serve you.

01:20:27.160 --> 01:20:27.760
" And it was straight-up demonic, this experience.

01:20:27.760 --> 01:20:31.510
But he was offering all this stuff, right?

01:20:37.040 --> 01:20:39.908
And as I was praying in the spirit, nothing moved as I was praying.

01:20:39.908 --> 01:20:51.582
But the moment I spoke the word, the moment I started quoting this scripture, the moment I started speaking in tongues and praying in the spirit and adding scripture to it, I started building myself up.

01:20:51.582 --> 01:20:57.333
So praying in the spirit, praying in the spirit, boom, the glory came in and he shot out like a rocket.

01:20:57.333 --> 01:21:07.933
But it wasn't until I got the word down in the prayer that the manifestation of what I was believing for against the demonic happened.

01:21:07.933 --> 01:21:13.396
How many times does it happen over and over and over again?

01:21:26.852 --> 01:21:27.199
You just pray in the spirit.

01:21:27.199 --> 01:21:30.663
"Oh God, let's pray in the spirit," just walking around the house.

01:21:30.663 --> 01:21:32.856
"Oh, Father, I thank you concerning my finances.

01:21:32.856 --> 01:21:34.920
Oh, you're going to supply, Lord.

01:21:38.220 --> 01:21:38.550
" And you're all in worry.

01:21:43.760 --> 01:21:43.920
You're worrying.

01:21:47.067 --> 01:21:47.324
Take the care out of your prayer.

01:21:55.840 --> 01:21:56.387
Like Pastor Chip said, take the care out of your prayer.

01:22:06.720 --> 01:22:07.199
And the more you are in care concerning your finances, concerning—well, you know, "I got a bill due.

01:22:08.159 --> 01:22:14.297
I got the light bill due, and I got the rent due, and my baby needs a new pair of shoes.

01:22:14.297 --> 01:22:23.270
" You have all these needs and you're praying the need, and "I've got seed in the ground," but you're in worry and you're in fear.

01:22:23.270 --> 01:22:29.943
That's why I turn to a scripture and I start renewing my mind to it.

01:22:29.943 --> 01:22:36.587
"God has not given me a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a sound mind.

01:22:36.587 --> 01:22:38.880
" 2 Timothy 1:7.

01:22:38.880 --> 01:22:47.120
"My God shall supply all my needs according to his riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

01:22:47.120 --> 01:22:50.411
" I started reading those over and over again, and I read Deuteronomy 28.

01:22:50.411 --> 01:22:54.023
I even have it on Deuteronomy 28 right now.

01:22:54.023 --> 01:22:58.267
That's why as I flip it open, it's my flopping spot.

01:22:58.267 --> 01:23:03.440
It's because it's worn out there because I read it so much.

01:23:03.440 --> 01:23:05.870
Deuteronomy 28 is my favorite.

01:23:05.870 --> 01:23:12.256
Not the curses part after 16, but the blessing at 13—but I'm just saying, you read about the blessing.

01:23:16.743 --> 01:23:23.466
You read about it, and you meditate on it, and it becomes real to you.

01:23:30.994 --> 01:23:31.211
So I go around over our eBay totes or whatever I have.

01:23:31.211 --> 01:23:43.919
I use Deuteronomy 28 as my sword coming out of my mouth, believing in my heart that whatsoever things I desire when I pray, I believe I receive them, and I shall have them.

01:23:43.919 --> 01:23:45.239
Mark 11:24.

01:23:46.056 --> 01:23:47.943
So I'm speaking to the mountain.

01:23:47.943 --> 01:23:50.280
I'm speaking to that mountain of debt.

01:24:02.971 --> 01:24:05.215
I'm speaking to it and I'm saying, "You have to go.

01:24:05.215 --> 01:24:08.439
" I'm calling those things that be not as though they were.

01:24:08.439 --> 01:24:10.160
I'm calling it in just like you said.

01:24:18.880 --> 01:24:26.480
The Bible says I can have what the Bible says I can have and I can do what the Bible says I can do.

01:24:26.480 --> 01:24:27.806
There you go.

01:24:27.806 --> 01:24:29.1000
So I'm going to say that.

01:24:29.1000 --> 01:24:32.160
I'm going to believe God in my heart.

01:24:32.160 --> 01:24:36.339
I'm going to say that out of my mouth.

01:24:36.339 --> 01:24:38.196
I'm going to say Mark 11:24.

01:24:38.196 --> 01:24:47.030
So, I'm going to believe God for this and I'm going to use this scripture and I'm going to pray over my stuff.

01:24:55.199 --> 01:24:55.404
And that's what I do.

01:25:05.404 --> 01:25:05.662
And like I said, y'all, I'm a work in progress.

01:25:05.662 --> 01:25:07.540
That's what I do for healing.

01:25:07.540 --> 01:25:09.330
That's what I do for everything.

01:25:10.434 --> 01:25:14.489
And you find it and you go, "God, I'm standing on this because it's a promise.

01:25:15.480 --> 01:25:19.428
" And the more you do that, it becomes more and more real to you every single day.

01:25:21.085 --> 01:25:21.394
And that's what I'm saying.

01:25:21.703 --> 01:25:22.835
You have to practice.

01:25:23.093 --> 01:25:26.440
You have to speak the word out of your mouth.

01:25:28.777 --> 01:25:30.320
You have to say it out and believe it in your heart.

01:25:35.579 --> 01:25:35.869
Don't doubt.

01:25:46.020 --> 01:25:46.270
I said, "I doubt my doubt.

01:25:55.040 --> 01:25:55.348
" I'm not going to sit there and I'm not going to let this doubt rise up on the inside of me.

01:26:00.099 --> 01:26:02.640
Like I told y'all sitting in the back of that church when we went to that healing revival, "This is fake.

01:26:07.211 --> 01:26:07.577
" What?

01:26:07.577 --> 01:26:09.929
That's not my thought, "This is fake.

01:26:16.847 --> 01:26:17.055
This is put on.

01:26:17.055 --> 01:26:18.339
This is a performance.

01:26:18.339 --> 01:26:21.387
" That's not where that thought came from.

01:26:21.387 --> 01:26:26.640
That came right out of the pit of hell.

01:26:26.640 --> 01:26:31.463
That's not the way I believe in my heart.

01:26:31.463 --> 01:26:34.480
But the enemy came in with a whisper.

01:26:38.768 --> 01:26:39.120
And I was thinking, that sly devil, I have never thought that ever before.

01:26:39.120 --> 01:26:44.827
But it came in like that and tried to drop those thoughts in your head.

01:26:44.827 --> 01:26:46.720
"This healing is not for today.

01:26:46.720 --> 01:26:49.200
" Are you kidding me?

01:26:49.200 --> 01:26:51.591
Do you see what I'm saying?

01:26:51.591 --> 01:26:53.909
But he'll come and whisper in your ear.

01:26:53.909 --> 01:27:01.130
But you have to take captive your thoughts, cast down every high imagination that exalts itself above the word of God.

01:27:04.439 --> 01:27:15.360
And so that's what you're going to have to do because if it tried to come against me, folks—and I'll tell you, of anybody, I believe I have seen a lot and I've seen the other side.

01:27:15.360 --> 01:27:21.120
I've seen the silos full of body parts, and you go, "Whoa, I don't believe that.

01:27:21.120 --> 01:27:22.862
" I don't care what you believe.

01:27:22.862 --> 01:27:24.587
I'm trying to tell you something today to help you.

01:27:24.773 --> 01:27:26.080
You don't want to believe it?

01:27:26.080 --> 01:27:29.160
That's fine, but you're wasting your time on this channel.

01:27:29.160 --> 01:27:32.331
I'm believing God for it, and I've seen the body parts.

01:27:33.062 --> 01:27:34.159
I've seen the glory.

01:27:34.159 --> 01:27:46.880
I've seen what's about to take place with the presence that God has for us—a major, major move of God with the pillars of fire, these Shekinah glory spots like Jacob's ladder where there's a major, major move...

01:27:46.880 --> 01:27:59.119
Remember I said this is how it went, and there's a lot of you that are new here, but I saw the Father and he put his hand out, and shafts of light came out of his fingers in this vision that I had.

01:27:59.119 --> 01:28:13.413
And each one of them made a crop—like, you know, like you see these crop circles that are—I believe they were kind of weird, you know, like that's what it looked like, but it was like a harvest area.

01:28:15.530 --> 01:28:19.440
And they were all throughout the United States and around the world, these pillars.

01:28:23.420 --> 01:28:24.500
And they were like Azusa Street revivals, okay?

01:28:24.500 --> 01:28:29.120
But they were not just one place in California; there were multiple places.

01:28:29.120 --> 01:28:36.520
But they went out of all his fingers, and they were designated areas for major revival, and he called them hot spots.

01:28:36.520 --> 01:28:37.090
Does anybody remember this?

01:28:37.090 --> 01:28:38.027
Some of you might.

01:28:38.027 --> 01:28:42.600
But the glory came out of his fingers, and there were pillars of fire.

01:28:43.600 --> 01:28:45.573
And the Lord told me in this, he said, "Do you see those places, Brandon?

01:28:45.573 --> 01:28:54.960
Those are where the end-time revivals, like Holy Ghost Woodstock, are going to take place all around the world.

01:29:01.839 --> 01:29:02.159
" And as the people came into those areas and in those neighborhoods, they fell out in the glory and they were healed.

01:29:02.159 --> 01:29:13.412
And he said before, with Oral Roberts and Jack Coe and all these others, God had to share, kind of like, the glory—He never shares anything—but, you know, people always go, "Oh, brother, you prayed for me and I got healed, right?

01:29:13.412 --> 01:29:14.693
It's because of your ministry.

01:29:17.120 --> 01:29:18.582
" The Lord said, "I'm not going to share my glory with anybody.

01:29:20.106 --> 01:29:22.800
" And you're going to see the demonstrations and manifestations like you have never seen before.

01:29:29.150 --> 01:29:29.360
And as people just show up in these places and just start to worship, the glory came on them and healed them.

01:29:29.360 --> 01:29:32.969
Whatever they needed—I saw limbs coming out, their arms, eyes popping open, ears.

01:29:32.969 --> 01:29:34.810
I'm talking a major move of God.

01:29:37.000 --> 01:29:42.267
And you know what happened was there were people that were just assigned to be there and say, "This is that.

01:29:42.267 --> 01:29:44.057
God showed up.

01:29:51.771 --> 01:29:51.943
This is the Lord, the power of the Lord.

01:29:51.943 --> 01:29:56.255
This is the end time," you know, like giving them an explanation of how they just got healed.

01:29:56.255 --> 01:30:01.760
So it wasn't just, you know, they went off and didn't have an explanation of what happened to their life.

01:30:16.239 --> 01:30:16.639
That's what I'm trying to say.

01:30:24.667 --> 01:30:25.040
There was a move of God that happened in those areas.

01:30:26.720 --> 01:30:33.706
And there were people that were assigned to those areas in Branson, and Collinsville, and Minneapolis, and Fort Worth—all these areas where God said, "I'm going to do something like I've never done before.

01:30:41.131 --> 01:30:41.383
Oh, I do a new thing.

01:30:41.383 --> 01:30:45.200
" But who will want to take the land for Jesus in these last days?

01:30:45.200 --> 01:30:49.920
Well, the elders say, "Well, we've always done it this way.

01:30:49.920 --> 01:30:53.840
We've got to try to hold it back and do it always like this.

01:30:55.646 --> 01:30:59.079
" And the Lord told me, he said, "Brandon, it will be like you've never seen it before.

01:30:59.079 --> 01:31:03.120
It's time to expect something you've never seen before to witness.

01:31:03.312 --> 01:31:08.560
You know, everybody, you get, like I said, people fall out and you don't know if it's real sometimes or not.

01:31:11.537 --> 01:31:11.742
They give you a courtesy fall is what I call them.

01:31:12.720 --> 01:31:14.709
" And they may shake a little bit and you go, "Okay, that's just flesh.

01:31:19.720 --> 01:31:21.750
" But you are about to see something that God is going to show up and show off in your life.

01:31:21.750 --> 01:31:23.787
And you're going to know it's God.

01:31:23.787 --> 01:31:25.920
You're just going to know.

01:31:25.920 --> 01:31:27.360
It's authentic.

01:31:27.360 --> 01:31:31.474
It's like we were talking—Diana saw this lady before and she said, "Everybody's just looking for authentic.

01:31:34.960 --> 01:31:35.190
" The world is what I'm talking about.

01:31:38.350 --> 01:31:38.660
The barbers, the beauticians are just looking for authentic.

01:31:39.280 --> 01:31:41.380
The gas clerks are looking for authentic.

01:31:41.380 --> 01:31:46.960
People in the hood are wanting authentic, a move of God like we've never seen before.

01:31:59.439 --> 01:32:00.079
And it's going to come through a shaking to awaken.

01:32:00.079 --> 01:32:02.959
It's going to come through a shaking to awaken.

01:32:04.200 --> 01:32:10.360
I saw the Bloods and the Crips and the bikers all coming to the glory of God and at the front of the church and giving their heart to Jesus Christ.

01:32:13.006 --> 01:32:13.160
And the Lord said, "Brandon, they're not just coming in with fishing poles anymore.

01:32:13.160 --> 01:32:14.338
They're coming in by the netfuls.

01:32:14.338 --> 01:32:19.920
" For there will be a moment in time everything will change in a 24-hour period just like it did with 9/11.

01:32:19.920 --> 01:32:21.040
9/11 changed everything.

01:32:21.760 --> 01:32:25.210
And he said to me, "There's going to be a major event in the spirit realm.

01:32:25.210 --> 01:32:27.260
Everything's going to change.

01:32:35.600 --> 01:32:35.902
" And I have an expectation that it's this year.

01:32:39.371 --> 01:32:43.467
I have an expectation that it's going to be around September the 23rd that we're going to start to see something major.

01:32:54.639 --> 01:32:54.856
He said the people in the days ahead will have to resist healing if they don't want to be healed if they come in these services.

01:32:54.856 --> 01:32:55.942
"I don't want it.

01:32:55.942 --> 01:33:06.720
" Now I don't know what kind of bozo would want to do that, but I'm going to tell you that tapping into the spirit, the Lord said, will be as easy as a bird flies in the air, as a fish swims in the water.

01:33:06.720 --> 01:33:09.049
Brother Hagin gave that word.

01:33:09.049 --> 01:33:15.075
But the Lord spoke to me, and I didn't even know that Brother Hagin had the word.

01:33:15.075 --> 01:33:23.311
And he said it to me, but he said, "It will be as easy as taking a breath.

01:33:23.311 --> 01:33:29.440
" As easy as taking a breath will be to tap into the anointing and to do things.

01:33:34.080 --> 01:33:34.380
And you're going to see things like you've never seen before.

01:33:34.380 --> 01:33:43.235
So, I just want you all to have—I'm just trying to stir you up a little bit to have that expectation for God to show up in your life.

01:33:43.235 --> 01:33:47.720
There's so many people that are so dry and so thirsty.

01:33:47.720 --> 01:33:50.605
I've seen it, especially at that meeting this week.

01:33:53.130 --> 01:33:54.669
People are just dry and they're going, "Man, I have all this stuff.

01:33:54.669 --> 01:33:57.029
" And I'm thinking, "Yeah, but Jesus has the answer.

01:33:57.029 --> 01:33:58.789
" Not Brandon, not Diana.

01:33:58.789 --> 01:34:00.400
Jesus has the answer.

01:34:12.800 --> 01:34:13.200
And there's no shortcuts.

01:34:13.200 --> 01:34:14.629
There's no cheating.

01:34:25.371 --> 01:34:25.520
You know, like we say, "Well, there's no...

01:34:26.400 --> 01:34:28.915
" It's like a microwave.

01:34:28.915 --> 01:34:41.993
Everybody thinks it's a microwave.

01:34:41.993 --> 01:34:49.520
No, it's an Easy-Bake Oven.

01:34:49.520 --> 01:35:03.600
It's your slow cooker, and you've got to put it in the scripture.

01:35:03.600 --> 01:35:06.820
You've got to put it in.

01:35:50.239 --> 01:35:50.529
And it's not a one-and-done.

01:35:50.529 --> 01:36:00.080
How bad do you want your life to change and go from glory to glory and not be the same anymore?

01:36:00.080 --> 01:36:04.266
Well, you can't be spiritually lazy.

01:36:04.266 --> 01:36:12.533
"Well, you know, I tried it a couple times and I read my Bible one time, brother, and I didn't see change.

01:36:12.533 --> 01:36:13.333
" It's consistency.

01:36:13.333 --> 01:36:15.626
How bad do you want change?

01:36:18.800 --> 01:36:20.340
And you see it a little bit at a time.

01:36:20.340 --> 01:36:31.120
First you see the blade, then you see the ear, then you see the full manifestation, but you've got to water it, and you've got to nurture it.

01:36:31.120 --> 01:36:34.120
Just like a farmer prays over his crops.

01:36:34.120 --> 01:36:42.089
I'm sure he's out there going, "Man, I need that corn to get up.

01:36:46.112 --> 01:36:46.536
" But he's not stressing out unless there's a drought.

01:36:46.536 --> 01:36:52.400
He just knows that he planted the seed and he's believing God for the increase.

01:37:05.880 --> 01:37:06.460
And he's out there and he checks on it, making sure the crows are not in it or whatever.

01:37:06.460 --> 01:37:09.156
So, you've got to maintain your seed.

01:37:09.156 --> 01:37:11.049
That's what I'm trying to say.

01:37:11.049 --> 01:37:12.760
You've got to quote the word over it.

01:37:12.760 --> 01:37:13.440
You've got to pray.

01:37:13.440 --> 01:37:31.249
You've got to go out there and maybe put some spiritual Roundup on some weeds, casting down some stuff.

01:37:46.860 --> 01:37:47.240
"I bind you in the name of Jesus off my harvest.

01:37:47.240 --> 01:37:51.679
You let it go, devil, in the name of Jesus.

01:37:55.253 --> 01:37:55.520
I call those things that be not as though they were.

01:38:00.520 --> 01:38:00.900
" And I say, "I'm blessed in the city.

01:38:00.900 --> 01:38:02.580
I'm blessed in the field.

01:38:02.580 --> 01:38:06.720
I'm blessed coming in and I'm blessed going out.

01:38:20.360 --> 01:38:20.720
I'm healed in my body.

01:38:20.720 --> 01:38:22.880
I'm delivered in my body.

01:38:22.880 --> 01:38:26.371
I'm not moved by what I see.

01:38:26.371 --> 01:38:29.120
I'm not moved by what I feel.

01:38:29.120 --> 01:38:34.800
I'm moved by what the word of God says.

01:38:39.268 --> 01:38:39.816
" And He said, "By His stripes, I am healed.

01:38:39.816 --> 01:38:42.986
He was wounded for my transgressions.

01:38:42.986 --> 01:38:49.546
He was bruised for my iniquities.

01:38:59.270 --> 01:38:59.500
The chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes, we are healed.

01:38:59.500 --> 01:39:08.288
" See, even I get it—I've quoted that probably two or three thousand times or more, and I mess up right then.

01:39:08.288 --> 01:39:09.024
See, it's real.

01:39:09.024 --> 01:39:10.436
But you just keep going.

01:39:17.712 --> 01:39:18.024
And I'm not kidding, that's one of my favorite verses.

01:39:19.888 --> 01:39:22.263
You just keep going over it and over and over and over it.

01:39:22.263 --> 01:39:27.659
So, what are they saying in the comment section?

01:39:27.659 --> 01:39:30.380
Yes, they memorize Psalms 24 and 93.

01:39:30.380 --> 01:39:35.280
Yeah, Psalm—yeah, "I pray deep roots in my spirit.

01:39:35.280 --> 01:39:37.269
" Psalms 91, mhm, Psalms 23.

01:39:37.269 --> 01:39:49.680
I told you in the days ahead, if you don't have it in your heart, there's a lot of you that will not make it in the days ahead for what I've seen coming.

01:39:53.360 --> 01:39:57.839
And I don't say that to scare you.

01:39:57.839 --> 01:39:59.929
I say that to prepare you.

01:40:09.400 --> 01:40:09.600
You need to know a great shaking is coming.

01:40:09.600 --> 01:40:11.440
I'm just being real with y'all.

01:40:11.440 --> 01:40:17.440
There's a major shaking that's about to take place beyond anybody's comprehension.

01:40:17.440 --> 01:40:23.600
And the Lord told me, he said, "You must remain filled with the Holy Spirit like you've never been before.

01:40:23.600 --> 01:40:25.050
Being filled, being filled.

01:40:25.050 --> 01:40:27.120
Do not become spiritually dry.

01:40:27.120 --> 01:40:28.719
" Yeah, I'm complacent.

01:40:28.719 --> 01:40:30.079
"Drink, drink, drink.

01:40:32.457 --> 01:40:38.436
" I even told a prophetic friend, "You're dumping out, dumping out, and dumping out all the time.

01:40:38.436 --> 01:40:40.124
You're dumping out, sir.

01:40:53.690 --> 01:40:54.182
But the Lord told me to call and tell you, you need to drink, drink, drink.

01:41:00.046 --> 01:41:00.320
You can dump out and tell everybody about Jesus all the time, but your water level gets low.

01:41:01.020 --> 01:41:03.919
You get out there and you're just talking out of dryness.

01:41:14.080 --> 01:41:18.040
" And the Lord told me you have to take times of refreshing and drink, drink, and have that spiritual Holy Ghost thermostat inside because with our flesh, you know when it's time to eat.

01:41:18.040 --> 01:41:39.859
Your body tells you, or you'll wake up and you'll say, "I feel like my mineral levels are low," or you think, "I need to take a certain vitamin," or you think, "I haven't gone to the bathroom in a while," so you take something for that.

01:41:39.859 --> 01:41:54.360
But it's just using the Holy Spirit to say—the Holy Spirit tells you, "Your worship level's low, your word level's low," and just following the Holy Ghost.

01:41:54.360 --> 01:41:59.209
Your flesh tells you, "I'm cold, I need a jacket.

01:41:59.209 --> 01:42:04.169
" Your spirit's speaking, but you've killed it because you haven't taken care of it.

01:42:04.169 --> 01:42:09.740
Your flesh gets usually three meals, two meals maybe, and some snacks a day.

01:42:09.740 --> 01:42:12.639
You listen to your flesh the moment it starts speaking.

01:42:12.639 --> 01:42:15.929
Yes, people don't listen to the Holy Spirit.

01:42:15.929 --> 01:42:17.280
No, but your spirit—you're a speaking spirit.

01:42:17.280 --> 01:42:24.720
I'm telling you, the spirit realm is more real than the natural.

01:42:24.720 --> 01:42:27.951
But just because you can't see it...

01:42:27.951 --> 01:42:29.920
But the moment is it.

01:42:29.920 --> 01:42:34.266
Tell them more.

01:42:34.266 --> 01:42:34.977
Yes.

01:42:34.977 --> 01:42:45.716
So a lot of times I'll wake up and I've been in the word a lot, but the next day I'll be like, I'll hit that, you know, where you're like, "I need something.

01:42:45.716 --> 01:42:46.427
" What is it?

01:42:46.427 --> 01:42:52.940
And the Holy Spirit rises up in me and he'll say, "Diana, you need to get in worship today.

01:42:52.940 --> 01:42:54.299
Get in worship.

01:42:54.299 --> 01:43:02.960
" And then sometimes he'll say, "You need to praise more," because I've been in worship so long and he'll say, "Praise.

01:43:13.449 --> 01:43:13.618
You need to praise.

01:43:13.618 --> 01:43:17.040
" So then, you know, sometimes it'll be just using him as a gauge.

01:43:18.495 --> 01:43:20.799
The Holy Spirit tells you where to go day to day.

01:43:20.799 --> 01:43:23.600
It's custom for you.

01:43:35.199 --> 01:43:36.159
And so, because he's here to lead and guide us into all truth, he's directing us to Jesus, constantly saying, "Today you need the word, Diana, for your circumstance, what you're going through today, what you're feeling.

01:43:44.880 --> 01:43:45.093
" Because we all wake up with these feelings and you're thinking, "What is this that I'm feeling?

01:43:45.093 --> 01:43:46.753
How do I get through this?

01:43:46.753 --> 01:43:51.220
" You're thinking, "How do I keep fighting this good fight of faith?

01:44:00.740 --> 01:44:00.920
" And he's there to lead and guide us, and we use him.

01:44:00.920 --> 01:44:01.640
We use discernment.

01:44:01.640 --> 01:44:02.959
He's there to help us.

01:44:02.959 --> 01:44:03.908
He's our helper.

01:44:03.908 --> 01:44:05.280
He comes to our aid.

01:44:05.280 --> 01:44:10.183
So that's just how we keep on fighting the good fight of faith.

01:44:10.183 --> 01:44:14.303
We find His grace to keep going.

01:44:14.303 --> 01:44:15.864
That's how we go.

01:44:15.864 --> 01:44:17.166
That's exactly right.

01:44:17.166 --> 01:44:25.000
And if you don't do that, you're going to be a spiritual wimp.

01:44:25.000 --> 01:44:25.400
Yes.

01:44:39.476 --> 01:44:45.990
And when the devourer comes to your house and starts knocking on your door, he'll come in and eat you.

01:44:45.990 --> 01:44:46.770
Yeah.

01:44:46.770 --> 01:44:51.395
But the Bible says the enemy comes in like a roaring lion.

01:44:54.959 --> 01:44:55.139
He's walking about seeking whom he may devour, right?

01:45:01.800 --> 01:45:02.070
And the only one that he can devour is the one that's not being spiritually up on their game.

01:45:09.320 --> 01:45:09.630
And a lot of people won't even let their hunger level go for their flesh that long.

01:45:11.520 --> 01:45:16.1000
So, at that first sign of hunger, like that stomach growling, they're like, "I need food.

01:45:16.1000 --> 01:45:21.360
" So they go and eat right away.

01:45:21.360 --> 01:45:44.658
But when you have that first—just that, because the Holy Spirit is such a gentleman, and it's just that still small voice inside of you, and that leading, he leads you and you feel that pull, that inward tug to go, "This is what you need.

01:45:46.080 --> 01:45:48.766
This is the direction you should go today.

01:46:10.880 --> 01:46:11.109
" And whenever you yield to that, and you yield to him, then it grows.

01:46:11.109 --> 01:46:16.983
It grows and grows and grows in you because you're yielding to it.

01:46:16.983 --> 01:46:23.280
So, just like you yield to the flesh and you say, "I need food.

01:46:23.280 --> 01:46:29.439
" At the first sign, you don't even let it go very long to that full-blown rumbling hunger.

01:46:31.725 --> 01:46:35.290
It's just that first little shakiness and you're like, "Oh, I need food.

01:46:35.290 --> 01:46:38.560
" So, it's the same way with your spiritual side.

01:46:38.560 --> 01:46:43.451
At that first sign, you say, "This is what I need.

01:46:43.451 --> 01:46:46.036
I'm yielding to the Holy Spirit.

01:46:46.036 --> 01:46:47.989
" You're yielding to him constantly.

01:46:47.989 --> 01:46:55.128
Just as you feel that shakiness and say, "I need food," you yield to the Holy Spirit.

01:46:56.864 --> 01:46:57.112
And how do you become familiar?

01:46:57.112 --> 01:46:59.900
How do you know what you need, though?

01:47:11.955 --> 01:47:12.239
Well, the more you yield to him, the more you know.

01:47:12.239 --> 01:47:13.860
He'll lead and guide you.

01:47:13.860 --> 01:47:14.400
Yeah.

01:47:14.400 --> 01:47:22.680
It's more like, "How do I know I need this drink of water versus maybe some vegetables?

01:47:22.680 --> 01:47:24.800
" You just know hunger versus thirst.

01:47:34.400 --> 01:47:34.690
There are things in the spirit: "I'm thirsty.

01:47:34.690 --> 01:47:35.560
I'm hungry.

01:47:35.560 --> 01:47:40.470
" You'll learn to develop your spirit, and you'll go right now.

01:47:40.470 --> 01:47:45.480
Drinking of the water of the word, eating of the meat of the word, worship and praise.

01:47:45.480 --> 01:47:52.820
You're drinking and filling yourself back up, and you get into that flow where you're feeding your spirit.

01:47:52.820 --> 01:47:54.080
You're drinking, and you're strong.

01:48:01.840 --> 01:48:10.469
And when the devil comes up there like a roaring lion, seeking whom he may devour, he comes to your house and he goes, "I got to get out of here.

01:48:20.418 --> 01:48:20.693
" You know why?

01:48:21.886 --> 01:48:24.613
Because he knows that you've got your full armor on.

01:48:25.413 --> 01:48:28.871
You've got your sword of the Spirit, and you're ready to cut his head off like Goliath.

01:48:29.449 --> 01:48:31.378
And he's going, "I came to the wrong house today.

01:48:34.000 --> 01:48:34.251
" Yes.

01:48:34.251 --> 01:48:36.592
"I came to the wrong house today.

01:48:38.770 --> 01:48:39.080
You better not mess with me.

01:48:39.080 --> 01:48:39.700
" Yeah.

01:48:43.920 --> 01:48:44.240
"Don't be coming to my door.

01:48:48.880 --> 01:48:49.129
" And he runs off.

01:48:49.129 --> 01:48:55.295
But he's only going to run off if you've got your armor on and you know who you are.

01:48:55.295 --> 01:49:01.253
If you've just got your sword up there and maybe nothing else on, he goes, "Ah, I've got dinner today.

01:49:01.253 --> 01:49:01.715
" Yeah.

01:49:01.715 --> 01:49:03.969
I mean, you know, he's the big bad wolf.

01:49:03.969 --> 01:49:09.119
So, and like I said, I don't ever really talk about the devil very often.

01:49:09.119 --> 01:49:11.531
I don't give him any place.

01:49:11.531 --> 01:49:15.051
I give no place to the devil by talking about him.

01:49:27.360 --> 01:49:27.582
I really don't.

01:49:30.080 --> 01:49:31.280
I don't even talk about that story I just told you all very often.

01:49:31.280 --> 01:49:38.560
But because I don't allow him to try to get that much real estate in my mind, meditating on him and thinking about him—he's defeated.

01:49:38.560 --> 01:49:39.240
Yes.

01:49:39.240 --> 01:49:43.080
So, why would you talk about somebody who's already been defeated that much?

01:49:43.080 --> 01:49:57.360
I remind him of his defeat and I remind him of his future all the time, but I'm not going to give him real estate in my mind to sit there and start because he's not paying rent, you know, by tormenting.

01:49:57.360 --> 01:49:58.480
Fear has torment.

01:50:00.120 --> 01:50:02.159
And he'll always try to play fear's greatest hits: "The what-ifs.

01:50:02.159 --> 01:50:03.120
" "What if?

01:50:03.120 --> 01:50:04.080
What if?

01:50:04.080 --> 01:50:04.640
What if?

01:50:04.640 --> 01:50:10.000
" You know, he comes up there and puts his greatest hits in your mind all the time.

01:50:10.000 --> 01:50:10.994
"What if?

01:50:10.994 --> 01:50:12.733
What if this happens?

01:50:25.449 --> 01:50:25.618
What if that?

01:50:29.093 --> 01:50:29.307
" And it continually bombards your thoughts.

01:50:41.716 --> 01:50:42.044
And those are the thoughts of fear coming against your head.

01:50:52.782 --> 01:50:58.080
And that's why I told Diana, I said, "I don't know, he's trying to come in.

01:50:58.080 --> 01:51:00.320
" Well, my word level is low.

01:51:00.320 --> 01:51:04.320
I've got to spend more time in the word today.

01:51:19.840 --> 01:51:20.240
So, I don't know, hopefully this is helping you all.

01:51:34.102 --> 01:51:34.525
We try to give you things that we work through.

01:51:41.537 --> 01:51:41.812
And Diana and I, like I said, we're a work in progress, but this is how we get through it.

01:51:41.812 --> 01:51:42.363
Yes.

01:51:52.719 --> 01:51:52.911
And we're a work in progress just like everybody else.

01:51:52.911 --> 01:51:56.290
But I'm going to tell you, this is where I see fruit.

01:52:00.914 --> 01:52:04.480
And if you listen to what we're telling you, you don't have to go around the mountain fifty billion times until you catch on and get a hold of something.

01:52:14.160 --> 01:52:19.420
I said, "Well, I wish somebody, when Megan was first diagnosed with autism, I just wish somebody that was a veteran in this could have come by and told us, 'Don't go down this road.

01:52:19.420 --> 01:52:23.493
Don't go down that road,' because we did it by trial and error.

01:52:23.493 --> 01:52:27.920
" And what we're telling you right now is years and years and years of experience.

01:52:39.960 --> 01:52:40.180
And you say, "Well, that's simple.

01:52:40.180 --> 01:52:42.053
" Well, to a baby Christian, it isn't.

01:52:42.053 --> 01:52:44.599
To somebody who's just trying to figure it out.

01:52:44.599 --> 01:52:52.239
Heartache is how we learned it—years and years of just getting a hold of the word and saying, "Listen, we're going to live this out.

01:52:52.239 --> 01:52:56.080
We're going to walk by faith and not by sight.

01:52:56.080 --> 01:53:02.639
I'm going to live, and I'm going to be on the victory side of things.

01:53:02.639 --> 01:53:06.540
" It's like we heard, "Better to stumble in faith than to sit in doubt.

01:53:06.540 --> 01:53:06.960
" Yeah.

01:53:06.960 --> 01:53:09.222
It's my new favorite thing.

01:53:09.222 --> 01:53:11.382
I heard it from Billy Burke.

01:53:11.382 --> 01:53:16.800
He said, "Better to stumble in faith than to sit in doubt.

01:53:22.959 --> 01:53:23.279
" And I said, "Oh, that is so good.

01:53:23.279 --> 01:53:24.560
" Run with that.

01:53:24.560 --> 01:53:25.543
So good.

01:53:25.543 --> 01:53:26.205
Yeah.

01:53:26.205 --> 01:53:27.462
I like it.

01:53:27.462 --> 01:53:28.514
Say it again.

01:53:28.514 --> 01:53:29.520
That's a t-shirt.

01:53:29.520 --> 01:53:33.840
"Better to stumble in faith than it is to sit in doubt.

01:53:33.840 --> 01:53:34.525
" Yeah.

01:53:34.525 --> 01:53:38.640
Oh, man, that got me all fired up when I was sitting there.

01:53:46.114 --> 01:53:46.389
I am not going to sit.

01:53:46.389 --> 01:53:48.880
I'd rather stumble in faith than to sit in doubt.

01:53:48.880 --> 01:53:54.880
I'm not going to sit there and just be a whiner about things.

01:54:09.440 --> 01:54:09.980
It's not going to change anything.

01:54:09.980 --> 01:54:16.560
Feeling down about yourself and feeling like, "Oh, I can't get through this," it's not going to change anything.

01:54:16.560 --> 01:54:17.959
And, quite frankly, nobody really cares.

01:54:17.959 --> 01:54:19.059
I'll be real.

01:54:20.260 --> 01:54:23.326
If you're the only one wallowed in self-pity, it isn't going to get any better.

01:54:23.326 --> 01:54:30.400
The only thing that's ever going to get you out of that self-pity and depression is the word of God.

01:54:38.120 --> 01:54:38.300
You can go to a counselor, but guess what?

01:54:38.300 --> 01:54:39.939
They're waiting for the next check.

01:54:39.939 --> 01:54:45.451
And you go in there and go, "I've got all this going on with me...

01:54:45.451 --> 01:54:47.893
" And they're going, "Oh, tell me more, brother.

01:54:47.893 --> 01:54:50.980
I'm having a hard time.

01:54:50.980 --> 01:54:54.000
" "Well, maybe if you do this.

01:55:06.656 --> 01:55:12.000
" And they try to talk to you.

01:55:17.493 --> 01:55:17.609
And then afterwards, "Okay, well, that's, I don't know, say 100 bucks, 500 bucks.

01:55:17.609 --> 01:55:17.724
Thank you.

01:55:17.724 --> 01:55:18.845
See you next week.

01:55:18.845 --> 01:55:22.960
" But they're not doing really anything to fix it.

01:55:22.960 --> 01:55:35.383
I mean, they may help you a little bit so you don't self-harm yourself or whatever, but the bottom line of what I'm trying to tell you is that they're paid to get money.

01:55:49.920 --> 01:55:50.240
That's what they went to school for.

01:56:00.160 --> 01:56:00.320
They get money.

01:56:05.851 --> 01:56:12.720
The only thing that's ever going to set you free is you'll know the truth, and the truth will set you free—the truth of God's word.

01:56:12.720 --> 01:56:25.679
Bottom line, you get a foundation of this Bible inside of your heart, and that's what's going to set you free from a psychiatrist or anything else, from addiction.

01:56:27.119 --> 01:56:30.960
You just need one touch from the Holy Spirit.

01:56:30.960 --> 01:56:33.840
One touch, one thread.

01:56:33.840 --> 01:56:39.360
Just one thread, and he can change you from the inside out.

01:56:39.360 --> 01:56:40.960
Yes, that's what we go for, these touches.

01:56:53.160 --> 01:56:53.440
I was frustrated because I wanted to go down there, but there were so many people that had so much more need than what I did.

01:56:53.440 --> 01:56:55.200
So I sat in the back.

01:56:55.200 --> 01:57:01.371
I wanted to be a spiritual hog and go up there, pushing my way to the front.

01:57:01.371 --> 01:57:02.346
"Give me a touch.

01:57:08.280 --> 01:57:08.769
" And I saw so many people that were so broken.

01:57:08.769 --> 01:57:15.400
I thought, "My need is not at that level of need right now.

01:57:15.400 --> 01:57:17.020
" So I sat back there.

01:57:17.020 --> 01:57:19.559
"God, you can touch me right here.

01:57:19.1000 --> 01:57:23.748
Even if I don't make it to the front row and get my special...

01:57:23.748 --> 01:57:25.119
" And you know what?

01:57:41.840 --> 01:57:41.990
He touched me right where I was sitting.

01:57:41.990 --> 01:57:43.250
We don't seek man; we seek him.

01:57:43.250 --> 01:57:44.299
Yes, he's the one.

01:57:44.299 --> 01:57:47.650
So we always want to make that clear, too.

01:57:47.650 --> 01:57:50.034
Yes, but you're just looking for a touch from Jesus.

01:57:50.034 --> 01:57:53.246
Even just sitting in the atmosphere, that's what we did.

01:57:59.120 --> 01:57:59.440
He can come to the back row.

01:58:01.267 --> 01:58:01.653
He's on the back row.

01:58:01.653 --> 01:58:05.976
We were in the very—I'm talking, that's the God we serve.

01:58:05.976 --> 01:58:06.571
Yeah.

01:58:21.800 --> 01:58:22.080
Well, you don't have to be on the front row to get a touch from Jesus.

01:58:35.005 --> 01:58:35.290
You can be on the back row, but just have a heart of expectation on the back row.

01:58:40.160 --> 01:58:40.960
It's like that song, "The God of the mountain is still God in the valley.

01:58:47.440 --> 01:58:48.020
" And so, at the front, same as the back, he's there.

01:58:48.020 --> 01:58:50.710
Yeah, I like the splash zone though.

01:58:50.710 --> 01:58:51.280
I do.

01:58:51.280 --> 01:58:52.880
Yeah, I do like the splash zone.

01:58:52.880 --> 01:58:55.804
I like to see the killer whale.

01:58:55.804 --> 01:59:01.040
I like the splash zone, don't get me wrong, but if I'm not in the splash zone, I'm still in the auditorium.

01:59:03.109 --> 01:59:04.840
And I say, "Jesus, touch me right now.

01:59:04.840 --> 01:59:06.835
Still contending for my miracle.

01:59:06.835 --> 01:59:07.813
" Yeah, I'm still contending.

01:59:07.813 --> 01:59:09.360
I'm fighting the good fight.

01:59:10.320 --> 01:59:14.676
"God, I'm back here in the back, and you told me to pray for these people.

01:59:14.676 --> 01:59:14.923
Stir yourself up.

01:59:14.923 --> 01:59:18.446
Believe God for somebody else's miracle, and keep your eyes off yourself and watch what happens.

01:59:18.446 --> 01:59:22.390
" Father, I thank you that you're touching those people up on the front row.

01:59:22.390 --> 01:59:25.312
I thank you for the people that stand in line.

01:59:25.312 --> 01:59:27.488
They're going to get their breakthrough today.

01:59:27.488 --> 01:59:29.520
I stand in the gap with them.

01:59:29.520 --> 01:59:35.280
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you're the miracle-working, mountain-moving God, that you're in the very breath we're breathing in this atmosphere right now.

01:59:35.280 --> 01:59:40.309
Just breathing it in is changing us, and we're going from glory to glory, glory to glory.

01:59:40.309 --> 01:59:42.449
He's changing us, changing us, changing us.

01:59:42.449 --> 01:59:46.970
See, the atmosphere just shifted, and that's why I thought that was pretty neat.

01:59:46.970 --> 01:59:49.420
Did you feel that?

01:59:49.420 --> 01:59:51.140
It's a wind.

01:59:53.620 --> 01:59:53.880
I feel him.

01:59:53.880 --> 01:59:55.180
The atmosphere just shifted.

01:59:55.180 --> 01:59:56.460
Thank you, Father.

01:59:56.460 --> 01:59:57.819
He's so wonderful.

01:59:57.819 --> 01:59:58.776
Thank you, Father.

01:59:58.776 --> 02:00:09.350
"From glory to glory, he's changing us, changing us, changing us, into his likeness and image, to perfect in me the love of God shown to the world, for he's changing, he's changing me.

02:00:09.350 --> 02:00:13.500
" We ask you, Father, to touch them right where they are tonight.

02:00:13.500 --> 02:00:16.088
Every single one of them has something they need.

02:00:16.088 --> 02:00:19.199
But it's time to believe God for big.

02:00:20.570 --> 02:00:25.074
And you may be here tonight, and you don't even know him.

02:00:25.074 --> 02:00:27.086
You've heard a lot about him.

02:00:27.086 --> 02:00:30.413
You've heard a lot about the Lord, but does he know you?

02:00:30.413 --> 02:00:32.480
Does he know you?

02:00:32.480 --> 02:00:37.980
If you were to die tonight after hearing all that we've said, and you say, "Oh, all that sounds okay.

02:00:37.980 --> 02:00:38.880
Whatever, brother.

02:00:38.880 --> 02:00:39.440
" No.

02:00:39.440 --> 02:00:44.869
But the bottom line is what we're here for is for you, the unbeliever.

02:00:49.440 --> 02:00:52.480
And you're here, and you don't know Jesus, and he doesn't know you.

02:01:13.040 --> 02:01:13.190
And if you were to die tonight, where would you spend eternity?

02:01:13.190 --> 02:01:14.089
Where would you spend eternity?

02:01:23.210 --> 02:01:23.500
I have to ask you that.

02:01:32.080 --> 02:01:32.411
It's the most important thing.

02:01:32.411 --> 02:01:38.090
It's the most important thing I can ask you today: where will you spend eternity?

02:01:38.090 --> 02:01:43.417
I've heard many say there's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

02:01:43.417 --> 02:01:45.239
But this is—it's a true statement.

02:01:45.989 --> 02:01:57.940
The very shoes you put on today to go to work or do whatever tomorrow, the undertaker might be taking them off that night.

02:02:05.599 --> 02:02:05.759
You don't know.

02:02:05.759 --> 02:02:07.153
None of us are promised tomorrow.

02:02:07.153 --> 02:02:08.891
None of us.

02:02:24.925 --> 02:02:25.336
But Jesus is real to Diana and me.

02:02:25.336 --> 02:02:28.359
He's real to us.

02:02:28.359 --> 02:02:28.799
He visits us.

02:02:28.799 --> 02:02:39.566
We have more of a presence in our house than we have a lot of times when we go to these services.

02:02:55.259 --> 02:02:55.679
The manifested presence of God comes into our home like he just did for us because we make a place for him.

02:02:55.679 --> 02:02:58.159
He's more real to us than you are.

02:02:58.159 --> 02:03:03.120
Having a relationship is more real to us than having a relationship with a human.

02:03:03.120 --> 02:03:06.590
Humans will hurt you; he'll never hurt you.

02:03:18.429 --> 02:03:18.679
And if you're here tonight, you say, "I don't know any peace.

02:03:22.933 --> 02:03:23.111
I don't know any joy in my life.

02:03:23.111 --> 02:03:25.056
I'm on the verge of just ending it all.

02:03:25.956 --> 02:03:29.600
I can't keep going on the way I'm going because I'm hurting so bad inside.

02:03:41.920 --> 02:03:42.178
" And I know; I've been there.

02:04:01.058 --> 02:04:01.236
I was ready to drive my car off a bridge multiple times whenever I've been really low, but Jesus was always there for me.

02:04:01.236 --> 02:04:07.600
And you may be at that place in your life where you are ready to do away with yourself.

02:04:07.600 --> 02:04:09.800
You're ready to be done.

02:04:13.279 --> 02:04:13.759
"I can't live this anymore.

02:04:13.759 --> 02:04:19.463
I'm in that much pain in my insides, in my mind, in my will, in my thinking, whatever.

02:04:27.360 --> 02:04:27.657
" It's a torment, you know.

02:04:41.496 --> 02:04:41.874
But you came here out of desperation tonight.

02:04:52.906 --> 02:04:53.128
You came here sitting alone in your home, and you're thinking, "Is there anybody that cares?

02:04:53.128 --> 02:04:53.795
Is there anybody that loves me?

02:04:53.795 --> 02:04:59.599
" But we do, and we just felt inside that we were supposed to do this live broadcast for somebody tonight.

02:04:59.599 --> 02:05:09.211
But I believe whoever you are watching on the other side of this live right now, you're watching this, and you're just asking, "Would somebody just please pray for me?

02:05:09.211 --> 02:05:12.560
" But the first step I want you to know is to give your heart to Jesus Christ.

02:05:15.632 --> 02:05:15.776
I want you to surrender to him.

02:05:16.516 --> 02:05:22.368
I want him to know you, and the only way he will ever know you is if you ask him to be your Lord and personal Savior.

02:05:22.368 --> 02:05:24.445
He's at the door knocking right now.

02:05:26.049 --> 02:05:32.667
The Bible says that no man comes to the Father unless he's drawn by him, which means he's tugging at your heart.

02:05:33.538 --> 02:05:36.308
You feel that inside of you right now.

02:05:36.308 --> 02:05:40.330
You feel that maybe there's some hope in what he's saying.

02:05:40.330 --> 02:05:44.765
But he's at your door knocking right now as we speak.

02:05:44.765 --> 02:05:48.880
He's knocking on your door and he's saying, "Will you let me in?

02:05:48.880 --> 02:05:51.279
Will you let me in?

02:05:54.619 --> 02:05:56.920
" And all you have to do is open the door and say, "Jesus, I invite you in tonight.

02:05:57.150 --> 02:06:03.566
" You could be like that little child that has a broken car that looks like it's so broken and there's no way to fix it.

02:06:03.566 --> 02:06:11.787
And because you're a child, because you don't see all the ways around that little car, that remote control car, and all it needs is a new battery.

02:06:11.787 --> 02:06:20.329
All it needs is maybe a little hair taken out of the wheels or whatever because it's not working right.

02:06:20.329 --> 02:06:31.000
But as you take that broken car, your life, to the Father who made it, you say, "Dad, I'm broken.

02:06:31.000 --> 02:06:37.668
I need you to fix me.

02:06:37.668 --> 02:06:43.312
" He says, "I specialize in this, hun.

02:06:43.312 --> 02:06:45.584
I specialize in this, sir.

02:06:45.584 --> 02:06:48.480
I can fix it like that.

